// Copy this file to Developer.local.xcconfig and fill in your Apple Developer
// Team ID. Developer.local.xcconfig is gitignored so each developer uses their
// own team; the committed Developer.xcconfig #include?s it automatically.
DEVELOPMENT_TEAM =

// Bundle-id prefix for the app + extension. The committed default in
// Developer.xcconfig is the placeholder com.example.ezvpn, which is registered
// to no team and so builds only unsigned. To sign, set a prefix your team owns
// (the Network Extension requires explicit, non-wildcard App IDs, so this must
// be a real prefix, first-come-first-served across all Apple accounts):
// BUNDLE_ID_PREFIX = com.yourname.ezvpn
